{"type": "article", "id": 15940, "title": "动物戒指", "description": "", "date": "2015-10-12T07:11:05Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 7, "praise_count": 190, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702135547BeJ67Y35GoLNyAiT.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是一组以动物为主题的戒指，来自泰国 merry me。每一组戒指都有三个，同时佩戴在手上才能看出其中的故事。比如松鼠系列是戴在三只邻近的手指上，能看到正在偷吃松果的松鼠；而斑马、梅花鹿等系列则是在一只手指上戴三只戒指，可以调整角度组成不同的故事。戒指外层是火烤的珐琅彩，使戒指有一个亮丽的色彩。另外，每个戒指都有小的开口以适应尺码误差。<a href=\"http://pleasemerryme.taobao.com/category-654314965.htm?spm=a1z10.3-c.0.0.e2iN9L&amp;search=y&amp;catName=r+i+n+g+s++%BD%E4+%D6%B8\" target=\"_blank\">这里是淘宝链接。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143406zuLjJpqnYBUvcwPr.jpg\" width=\"721\" height=\"504\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.69902913\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143406gCJFswqlROyfuxDZ.jpg\" width=\"721\" height=\"449\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.62274619\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143407UXxbZrphlS5nBATu.jpg\" width=\"721\" height=\"330\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.45769764\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143407XUF94gELwpxrisWt.jpg\" width=\"721\" height=\"465\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.64493759\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261434082SUcRYmObf4xez51.jpg\" width=\"567\" height=\"567\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143408Ps4a5pefIhVWJuy6.jpg\" width=\"567\" height=\"567\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}